cu.explanation_en: Setting Asn1_verbosity to an invalid value will cause ASN.1 message parsing errors and prevent proper protocol message handling in the CU.

du.explanation_en: Setting Asn1_verbosity to an invalid value will cause ASN.1 message parsing errors and prevent proper protocol message handling in the DU.
du.explanation_zh: 將 Asn1_verbosity 設定為無效值會導致 ASN.1 訊息解析錯誤，並阻止 DU 中正確的協議訊息處理。
